			Company Description 


			Synergy Pharmaceuticals, Inc. is a biopharmaceutical company, which focuses on the development and commercialization of novel gastrointestinal therapies. Its product includes plecanatide and dolcanatide. The company was founded by Kunwar Shailubhai on November 15, 2005 and is headquartered in New Yo...
		


                Synergy Pharmaceuticals, Inc. is a biopharmaceutical company, which focuses on the development and commercialization of novel gastrointestinal therapies. Its product includes plecanatide and dolcanatide. The company was founded by Kunwar Shailubhai on November 15, 2005 and is headquartered in New York, NY.
            




